    <div class="body">
        <p>To my knowledge it's not possible to use the redirector together with hashes in an easy manner, eg. /post/view/id/12/#comment327</p>

<p>Apart from array('controller' =&gt; 'user', 'action' =&gt; 'view', 'useess' =&gt; '#hash') to generate "/user/view/useless/#hash", which isn't very nice, I don't think this is possible.</p>

